                     <interp inst="t18440506-1497-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18440506-1497-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> stealing 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of a certain man unknown, from his person; and that they had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
